ğŸ“ Where else can SQL injection happen?
You can inject SQL wherever user input reaches the database. For example:

Forms (like login or search fields)

Cookies

Headers (like User-Agent, Referer)

JSON data

XML data

API requests

If the backend reads that input and puts it into an SQL query â€” it's injectable!

